---
layout: layout-base.njk
title: Guides
description: Practical growing guides for short seasons.
---

<section class="card">
  <h2>Guides</h2>
  <p class="small" style="opacity:0.86;">Short, practical write-ups to help you make good decisions quickly.</p>

  {%- set guidePages = collections.all | selectattr("data.guide") -%}

  <ul class="list" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
    {%- for p in guidePages | sort(attribute="data.title") -%}
      <li class="note">
        <a href="{{ p.url }}"><strong>{{ p.data.title or p.fileSlug }}</strong></a>
        {%- if p.data.description -%}
          <div class="small" style="opacity:0.85; margin-top:0.25rem;">{{ p.data.description }}</div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </li>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </ul>
</section>
